name: RTCInboundRtpStreamStats.trackId
description: The trackId property of the RTCInboundRtpStreamStats dictionary indicates the id of the RTCReceiverAudioTrackAttachmentStats or RTCReceiverVideoTrackAttachmentStats object representing the MediaStreamTrack which is receiving the incoming media.
